| mitt_romney              |                   0.500 |          0.042 | Authentic Virtue         |             0.720 |                  0.720 |           0.180 |                0.240 |
| john_lewis               |                   0.253 |          0.020 | Virtue-Leaning           |             0.780 |                  0.730 |           0.400 |                0.430 |
